.demxButton button {
  font-family: 'Segoe UI Semibold', wf_segoe-ui_semibold, helvetica, arial, sans-serif;
  background-image: none;
  box-shadow: none;
  background-color: #C8C8C8;
  padding: 0px 17px;
  border: 2px solid #C8C8C8;
  border-radius: 0;
  text-shadow: none;
  font-size: 14px;
  width: auto;
  white-space: nowrap;
  color: #000;
  transition: color 0.2s, background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
}
.demxButton:active:hover button,
.demxButton:focus button,
.demxButton:focus:hover button,
.demxButton:hover button {
  border-color: #000;
  background-color: #F4F4F4;
  color: #000;
  outline: 0;
}
.demxButton:active button {
  background-color: #666;
  border-color: #666;
  color: #000;
}
.demxButton.primary button {
  background-color: #F2C811;
  border-color: #F2C811;
  color: #000;
}
.demxButton.primary:active button,
.demxButton.primary:focus button,
.demxButton.primary:hover button {
  border-color: #000;
  color: #000;
}
.demxButton.primary:active:hover button,
.demxButton.primary:focus:hover button {
  background-color: #CDA521;
}
.demxButton.disabled button,
.demxButton.disabled.primary button,
.demxButton[disabled] button,
.demxButton[disabled].primary button {
  background-color: #F4F4F4;
  border-color: #F4F4F4;
  color: #A6A6A6;
  cursor: default;
}
.demxButton.disabled.primary:active button,
.demxButton.disabled.primary:focus button,
.demxButton.disabled.primary:hover button,
.demxButton.disabled:active button,
.demxButton.disabled:focus button,
.demxButton.disabled:hover button,
.demxButton[disabled].primary:active button,
.demxButton[disabled].primary:focus button,
.demxButton[disabled].primary:hover button,
.demxButton[disabled]:active button,
.demxButton[disabled]:focus button,
.demxButton[disabled]:hover button {
  background-color: #F4F4F4;
  border-color: #F4F4F4;
  color: #A6A6A6;
}

.poGantt__spinner_icon,
.poGantt__spinner_icon:after {
  border-radius: 50%;
  width: 3em;
  height: 3em;
}
.poGantt__spinner_icon {
  font-size: 10px;
  position: relative;
  text-indent: -9999em;
  border-top: 1.1em solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-right: 1.1em solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-bottom: 1.1em solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-left: 1.1em solid #ffffff;
  -webkit-transform: translateZ(0);
  -ms-transform: translateZ(0);
  transform: translateZ(0);
  -webkit-animation: load8 1.1s infinite linear;
  animation: load8 1.1s infinite linear;
}
@-webkit-keyframes load8 {
  0% {
    -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);
    transform: rotate(0deg);
  }
  100% {
    -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);
    transform: rotate(360deg);
  }
}
@keyframes load8 {
  0% {
    -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);
    transform: rotate(0deg);
  }
  100% {
    -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);
    transform: rotate(360deg);
  }
}
.poGantt__spinner {

}
